# Film Recommendation Web Application

This project is a simple web application designed to provide film recommendations based on content-based filtering. The application helps users discover new movies by suggesting films similar to those they have enjoyed.

## Key Features

- **Content-Based Filtering:** Analyzes the films that users have liked and provides 10 personalized recommendations for similar movies.
- **User-Friendly Interface:** Developed using Python, Flask, and Scikit-learn, the application features an easy-to-navigate interface.

## Goal

The goal of this application is to offer users an easy way to find movies that match their tastes and preferences, enhancing their film-watching experience.
